QuestData.Title: WANTED: Sunseeker Channelers
QuestData.Description: It has been whispered to Mah'duun that the channelers of the military unit known as the Sunseekers must be killed today.$B$BThey are to be found within the Botanica at Tempest Keep.$B$BYou want the bounty, you kill the channelers.
QuestData.LogDescription: Nether-Stalker Mah'duun wants you to kill 6 Sunseeker Channelers. Return to him in Shattrath's Lower City once they all lie dead in order to collect the bounty.
QuestData.CompletionText: How can it be that we are speaking when the channelers are not all lying dead?
QuestData.RewardText: And now they are dead, channeling no longer. He who whispers upon the nether is satisfied and you have secured the bounty.$B$BReturn again tomorrow and the winds will have whispered once more to Mah'duun.
